that we'll get into later, and its subject matter,

70
00:04:50,202 --> 00:04:53,344
the Robert Johnson's partially self-constructed,

71
00:04:54,284 --> 00:04:58,386
semi-autobiographical legend of meeting a dark man at the crossroads

72
00:04:58,426 --> 00:05:02,508
to make a deal, a diabolic pact that would seal his musical fate,

73
