131
00:10:10,891 --> 00:10:15,474
nor was his ear less peeled with noises loud and ruinous.

132
00:10:17,792 --> 00:10:22,549
this inspiring power of the story of the Devil's Rebellion,

133
00:10:23,071 --> 00:10:24,034
the Rebel Angel.

134
00:10:24,749 --> 00:10:33,192
is a heavy metal archetype whose power has not been lost on heavy metal musicians and the creators of their visual art,

135
00:10:33,392 --> 00:10:34,933
their merchandise, and their posters.

136
00:10:35,433 --> 00:10:43,196
And while Led Zeppelin's poster may be as much the fall of Icarus as the fall of Lucifer,

137
00:10:43,616 --> 00:10:49,898
Black Sabbath has clearly embraced the Miltonic vision of the rebel angel.

138
00:10:50,887 --> 00:10:58,777
But these are all signs and portents foreshadowing the figure of Raziel, who was cast down from

139
00:10:58,877 --> 00:11:05,306
Soul Reaver 2, in which the generative power of Milton's song has become a reality.

