148
00:11:58,451 --> 00:12:05,294
possession and demonic imbuing of weapons that run throughout the multiverse of the

149
00:12:05,354 --> 00:12:09,655
Soul Reaver 2 series, infusing it with metal energy.

150
00:12:12,332 --> 00:12:19,137
