Here now, the Requiem of Blood in Castlevania, Rondo of Blood, Castlevania Drascula X,

241
00:18:46,598 --> 00:18:51,682
in which a naked succubus rides on the back of a skull that shoots laser beams.

242
00:18:54,319 --> 00:18:59,000
or in which our protagonist leaps on the back of a horse-drawn hearse

243
00:18:59,820 --> 00:19:03,081
