294
00:23:14,841 --> 00:23:18,805
It is ultimately the role of mechanics to energize the world.

295
00:23:19,426 --> 00:23:24,911
But we have to understand that for a level to be fully metal...

296
00:23:25,877 --> 00:23:29,800
It's not enough for the gameplay to be simply brutal,

297
00:23:29,860 --> 00:23:34,223
